# VEHICLE::SET_PLANE_ENGINE_HEALTH

## Summary
The same as the above function but it allows the engine health on planes to be set higher than the max health

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **FLOAT** health

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Works just like SET_VEHICLE_ENGINE_HEALTH, but only for planes.
